<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فِي كُلِّ يَوْمٍ لَنَا مَيِّتٌ نُشَيِّعُهُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>نَرَى بِمَصْرَعِهِ آثَارَ مَوْتَانَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يَا نَفْسُ مَإلى وَلِلأَمْوَالِ أَتْرُكُهَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>خَلْفِي وَأُخْرَجُ مِنْ دُنْيَايَ عُرْيَانَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَبَعْدَ خَمْسِينَ قَدْ قَضَيْتُهَا لِعِبَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>قَدْ آنَ أَنْ تَقْصُرِي قَدْ آنَ قَدْ آنَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مَا بِالُنَا نَتَعَامَى عَنْ مَصَائِرُنَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>نَنْسَى بِغَفْلَتِنَا مَنْ لَيْسَ يَنْسَانَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>نَزْدَادُ حِرْصًا وَهَذَا الدَّهْرُ يَزْجُرَنَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>كَانَ زَاجِرَنَا بِالْحِرْصِ أَغْرَانَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أَيْنَ الْمُلُوكُ وَأَبْنَاءُ الْمُلُوكِ وَمَنْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>كَانَتْ تَخِر لَهُ الأَذْقَانُ إِذْعَانَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>صَاحَتْ بِهِمْ حَادِثَاتُ الدَّهْرِ فَانْقَلَبُوا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مُسْتَبْدِلِينَ مِن الأَوْطَانِ أَوْطَانَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>خَلَّوا مَدَائِنَ كَانَ الْعِزُّ مَفْرَشُهَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَاسْتَفْرَشُوا حُفُرًا غُبْرًا وَقِيعَانَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>يَا رَاكِضًا فِي مَيَادِين الْهَوَى مَرِحًا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَرَافِلاً فِي ثِيَابِ الْغَيِّ نَشْوَانَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مَضَى الزَّمَانُ وَوَلَّى الْعُمْرُ فِي لَعِبٍ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>يَكْفِيكَ مَا قَدْ مَضَى قَدْ كَانَ مَا كَانَا ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>